


=Summary=

As proposed by the [[European Sharing Economy Coalition]]:


* Encourage urban agriculture by removing barriers to growing and selling. 

* Provide tax credits to property owners who farm vacant land. Conduct inventories that explore the potential for food cultivation on unused land. 

* Allow food distribution points to in­crease access to local food production. 

* Support the establishment of food redistribution programs. 

* Support local commercial kitchens and food enterprises.​


(http://www.euro-freelancers.eu/european-sharing-economy-coalition/)



